<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
December 5 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -5 degrees C., max. 3 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. -2 degrees C., max. 3 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. -2 degrees C., max. 4 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. -3 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., overcast to
sleet, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 6 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., drizzle to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 6 degrees C., max. 9 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 8 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing: min. 3 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, gentle to moderate breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min.7 degrees C., max. 12 degrees C., drizzle,
moderate to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 2 degrees C., max. 6 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 3 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
