cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 10 degrees C., max. 22 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 14 degrees C., max. 21 degrees C., cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze. 
</P>
