<HEADLINE> URGENT: India's Fresh Elections Starts from 3rd Week </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Election Commissioner G.V.G.
Krishnamurty said today that fresh Lok Sabha (Lower House of
Parliament) elections will be held between the third week of
February and first week of March next year.
</P>
<P>
His statement was made in the wake of President K.R.
Narayanan's announcement of dissolution of the 18-month old House
earlier today. 
</P>
