announced here today that it is enhancing services to its major
Southeast Asian destinations in a bid to recapture leadership in
its regional backyard.
</P>
<P>
From December 1, the national flag carrier will operate only
brand-new Airbus A320 aircraft on its five-times-a-week service to
Kuala Lumpur to replace the older A300s on the route, PAL said in
a press statement issued here.
</P>
<P>
