<HEADLINE> Roundup: India Strives to Eradicate Poverty </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 4 (Xinhua) -- The Indian government has
taken various measures to help poor and backward areas in the
country develop their economy in an effort to alleviate and
eradicate poverty.
</P>
<P>
