<HEADLINE> Myanmar Deputy Minister Meets Chinese Writers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar Deputy Information
Minister U Thein Sein met with a visiting Chinese writers
delegation here today.
</P>
<P>
