<HEADLINE> Panama, Ecuador Sign Cooperation Accord </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PANAMA CITY, December 3 (Xinhua) -- Panamanian Foreign Minister
Ricardo Alberto Arias and his counterpart in Ecuador, Jose Ayala
Lasso, signed an agreement today aimed at fostering cooperation in
culture, education, science, sports and the arts.
</P>
<P>
