at a propitious moment in our relations," the Ecuadoran foreign
minister said. He also noted that Ecuador was considering a
financial agreement on air cooperation, investments and taxes.
</P>
<P>
Both ministers are optimistic about the plans to conclude a
free trade agreement between Panama and the Andean
Community. 
