<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, December 3 (Xinhua) -- The 4th Joint Meeting between
Cuba and the Caribbean Community and Common Market (Caricom)
concluded today in Havana, after three days of discussions on ways
to boost bilateral ties.
</P>
