products which harm people and the environment.
</P>
<P>
Supported by leaders of the Catholic Church, the workers`
protests have diminished banana shipments to Europe.
</P>
<P>
Foreign Ministry`s Director of International Policy, Luis
Guillermo Solis, said that several meetings are being held to
outline a suitable strategy for the campaign with all sides
involved. 
